data.description: HORSE PROPERTY!! LOCATED IN THE DESIRABLE AREA OF APPLE VALLEY!!!   This immaculate 2505 sq ft 4-bedroom split floor plan which includes 2 primary bedrooms with its own en-suite bathrooms, is perfect for a guest suite's own private space.   You'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting living featuring a charming pellet wood stove encompassed by a beautiful layered brick wall that not only adds warmth but also creates a cozy place for the family and saves on the utility cost. It's the ideal spot to gather around with loved ones during chilly evenings.  The kitchen is complete with stainless steel appliances, ample counter space, and a beverage chiller and counter as well as a full dining area perfect for preparing family meals or hosting friends.   A shared Jack and Jill bathroom connects the other two bedrooms, with a beautiful half bathroom in the hall for convenience and a HUGE laundry room with a granite countertop, sink, and loads of cabinets.  The property sits on a ONE-ACRE lot, able to have a farm of animals horses, and a chicken coupe to bring your own chickens, goats, and more.   Ride your ATV’s  in the surrounding desert trails along with RV parking, with an OVER-SIZED THREE-CAR this lot offers a perfect balance of outdoor space for activities and relaxation and is surrounded by beautiful views of the natural desert landscape mountains, and AMAZING SUNRISES.  Whether you want to create your own garden oasis, set up a play area for the kids, or simply enjoy the serenity of the surroundings, this home provides endless possibilities.  Enjoy the hot summers with a POOL to relax in your private oasis along with a covered patio.  Other features include PRIVATE WELL WATER, which can be a cost-effective and an OVERSIZED PROPANE TANK that ensures you have plenty of fuel, a COST EFFECTIVE PELLET STOVE for those cold nights, and much much more!!  Close to schools, stores, medical facilities, and freeway for easy commuter access.  Don't miss the opportunity to make it your own and experience the best that Apple Valley has to offer. Schedule a viewing today and start envisioning your future in this exceptional property!
